description.raw:
**Ignore this pull request unless you're working on the foosball demo**

* Reduced duplicate code when creating teams

* Added comments

* Joints from each team face a different direction

* Removed handle collisions because I think they aren't necessary, but I can bring them back if you want

* There's a lot of indentation change, side-by-side diff recommended 

![joints.png](data/bitbucket.org/repo/EgGzpd/images/627972461-joints.png)
